<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en" ng-app="serverOrderApp" ng-controller="serverOrderCon">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport"
	content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/mui.min.css">
<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="../../css/style.css">
<script src="../../js/mui.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/angular.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/angular-sanitize.min.js"></script>
<script src="../../js/util.js"></script>
<title>确认订单</title>
</head>
<body class="notice_back" ng-cloak>
	<div class="doctor_top serve_top">
		<img ng-src="{{docUrl}}">
		<h3 ng-bind="docName"></h3>
		<p>
			{{infirmaryName}}<span>{{positionName}}</span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="serve_con">
		<h3 class="serve_line">
			<span class="left_icon"></span>
			<p ng-bind="serverName"></p>
			<p class="serve_money">
				¥{{price | number:2}}<i>/{{serverCount}}次</i>
			</p>
		</h3>
		<p class="serve_detail" ng-if="orderType==4">通过在线图文及语音与医生交流，为您订制调理方案。</p>
		<p class="serve_detail" ng-if="orderType==6">在线图文沟通症状，随时随地管理病情。</p>
		<p class="serve_detail" ng-if="orderType==7">结合在线图文，与医生电话沟通症状，获得订制调理方案。</p>
		<p class="serve_detail" ng-if="orderType==8">电话沟通病情，快速答疑解惑。</p>
	</div>
	<div class="serve_con serve_person" ng-click="checkAddr($event)">
		<h3 class="serve_line" ng-cloak ng-if="null==patientName">
			<span class="left_icon"></span>
			<p>选择就诊人</p>
		</h3>
		<p class="serve_message" ng-cloak ng-if="null!=patientName">
			<span ng-bind="patientName"></span> <span ng-bind="patientSex"></span>
			<span>{{patientAge}}岁</span> <span ng-bind="patientPhone"></span>
		</p>
	</div>
	<div class="affirm_express">
		<h3>
			<span class="left_icon"></span>温馨提示
		</h3>
		<ul ng-if="orderType==4">
			<li>1.您可通过图片、文字、语音的方式与医生进行交流，医生将为您开具调理方案。</li>
			<li>2.本次服务将在支付48小时后结束，支付后请根据平台提示进行操作。</li>
		</ul>
		<ul ng-if="orderType==6">
			<li>1.您可通过文字、图片的方式与医生进行交流，医生将为您答疑解惑。</li>
			<li>2.本次服务将在咨询次数用尽后或支付48小时后结束，支付后请根据平台提示进行操作。</li>
		</ul>
		<ul ng-if="orderType==7">
			<li>1.支付完成后您将收到平台由第三方（022-8210****）转接的电话，请注意接听。</li>
			<li>2.您还可通过文字、图片、语音的方式与医生进行交流，医生将为您开具调理方案。</li>
			<li>3.本次服务将在支付48小时后结束，支付后请根据平台提示进行操作。</li>
		</ul>
		<ul ng-if="orderType==8">
			<li>1.支付完成后您将接到平台回电，请保持手机畅通。</li>
			<li>2.回电将由第三方（022-8210****）进行转接，请注意接听。</li>
		</ul>
	</div>
	<div class="affirm_bot serve_bot">
		<h3>
			实付：<span ng-cloak>¥{{price | number:2}}</span>
		</h3>
		<button ng-click="addOrder()">确认订单</button>
	</div>
	<div class="mui-iframe-wrapper"
		style="top: 0px; bottom: 0px;height: 100%;background-color: #fff;overflow:hidden;display:none;z-index: 99999">
		<iframe src="../person/seedoctor_person.html?type=true"
			id="person_manage" name="person_manage"></iframe>
	</div>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/hospital/affirm_serverorder.js"></script>
	<script type="text/javascript" src="../../js/foot.js"></script>
</body>
</html>